  "content": "<p data-pid=\"q80PVcRL\">一种学习方法，指学生通过绘制一种「方框-箭头」式的图表来阐释某个主题，该图表旨在呈现核心概念/过程及其相互关系。</p><ul><li data-pid=\"otqRgciY\"><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//notes.andymatuschak.org/z3J3QxG3TkZfqkKWTx9cBvi\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">绘制概念图是否涉及内隐提取练习？</a><sup data-text=\"绘制概念图是否涉及内隐提取练习？\" data-url=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/1929183905371619597\" data-draft-node=\"inline\" data-draft-type=\"reference\" data-numero=\"1\">[1]</sup></li></ul><h2>参考文献</h2><ul><li data-pid=\"QdrLI7Pl\"><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//notes.andymatuschak.org/zKDWDVyZ7kBQLnq6Fq5KSj6\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">Blunt, J. R., &amp; Karpicke, J. D. (2014). Learning with retrieval-based concept mapping. Journal of Educational Psychology, 106(3), 849–858</a></li><ul><li data-pid=\"b0MGDmlu\">将绘制概念图用于<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//notes.andymatuschak.org/zXA8c6XtMLgRCGwJFGnZUvw\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">提取练习</a><sup data-text=\"提取练习\" data-url=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/1928747840647168044\" data-draft-node=\"inline\" data-draft-type=\"reference\" data-numero=\"2\">[2]</sup>时，其产生的<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//notes.andymatuschak.org/zTpJdbe6ub7uhBFLuHkFsrT\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">测试效应</a><sup data-text=\"测试效应\" data-url=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/423449068\" data-draft-node=\"inline\" data-draft-type=\"reference\" data-numero=\"3\">[3]</sup>并不比单纯写下回忆内容的效果更强。</li></ul><li data-pid=\"XZFptwiH\">O’Day, G. M., &amp; Karpicke, J. D. (2021). Comparing and combining retrieval practice and concept mapping. Journal of Educational Psychology, 113, 986–997.<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//doi.org/10.1037/edu0000486\" class=\" external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"><span class=\"invisible\">https://</span><span class=\"visible\">doi.org/10.1037/edu0000</span><span class=\"invisible\">486</span><span class=\"ellipsis\"></span></a></li><ul><li data-pid=\"EF5r3I7O\">「即便组合练习组的学生在学习材料上花费的时间，要显著多于单一练习组的学生，但『概念图与提取练习相结合』的练习方式，相比于『单纯的提取练习』，并未能产生任何额外的好处。」</li></ul></ul><h2><br/>链接至本文（已汉化）</h2><ul><li data-pid=\"nZUf-BIm\"><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/536670074\" class=\"internal\" target=\"_blank\">提取练习和迁移学习</a></li></ul><h2>声明</h2><p data-pid=\"a1kSLiu9\">此内容发布由 Andy Matuschak 许可。未经允许，不得转载或修改。保留所有权利。</p><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br/></p><blockquote data-pid=\"Yu6lrJBQ\"><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//paratranz.cn/projects/3131\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">Thoughts Memo</a> 汉化组译制<br/>感谢主要译者 gemini-2.5-pro，校对 Jarrett Ye<br/>原文：<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//notes.andymatuschak.org/z2crTaHNqd6APCtmzXk7x6W\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">Concept mapping</a></blockquote>",
